        },
        "subject": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Fix checking of peer field",
        "message": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Fix checking of peer field\n\nThe transaction debug and error print macros only check the\ntransaction peer field if it is NULL or not. There is a third state\nthe peer field can be which is error. Define the KFILND_TN_PEER_VALID\nmacro which can be used to verify the peer field is valid or not. It\naccounts for all three states.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-9343\nSigned-off-by: Ian Ziemba <ian.ziemba@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: Ibe2d51067db6dcf094eb3aae69a6a9aaef0f5d82\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
